{
  "text": "It is important to realise that dispersules may (occasionally) get transported by one of the above modes even though they have no obvious adaptation for it. This is particularly true for endo-zoochory and exo-zoochory (e.g. Fischer et al. 1996; [CITATION_1] . Note that there is ample literature (e.g. in Floras) for dispersal mode of many plant taxa.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "53332554"
